
SNOOP(2)                  SYSTEM CALLS                   SNOOP(2)

NAME
     snoop - "overrides the driver's snoop efun

SYNOPSIS
     varargs object snoop(object snooper, object snoopee);

DESCRIPTION
     This simul_efun overrides the driver's snoop function to add
     the following functionality:

     1)  Limits snooping to wizards and above.   2)   Admins  can
     snoop anybody.  3)  Non-admins can only snoop those who have
         "snoopable" set.  4)  If  the  "snoopee"  is  an  admin,
     notifies him
         or her that they are now being snooped by
         the "snooper".

